GIRARD AVE.', '#1014 South Facing Penthouse', 'Stunning Total Luxury Remodel 1bed/1bath on the 10th PENTHOUSE floor with views of CITY LIGHTS and the Rockies!', 'NEW LUXURY KITCHEN: High End Kitchen Kraft Soft Close Cabinets with Sparkle Finish Quartz Counter Tops with Marble Backsplash, KitchenAid Stainless Steel 3door Refrigerator, Self Cleaning Oven, Large Microwave, and Dishwasher, Oversize Undermount Composite Kitchen sink with Kohler PullOut Faucet, New High Grade carpet, and thick pad, 12x24 Brick set Ceramic tile floors.', 'NEW LUXURY BATH: Undermount China Sink with Kohler PullOut Bathroom Faucet, Sparkle Finish Quartz Counter Top with Marble Backsplash, All Marble Shower with Frameless European Thick Glass Doors, Soft Close Kohler Toilet.', ' Decorator Vertical window blinds, Modern light fixtures through out, Edison Bulbs.', ' Street parking available or pay extra to the property management company for inside garage space or outside building space.', 'Hot water heat and A/C, gas, and water are paid for by the Landlord - you only pay for electricity and cable.', 'Must have mid credit score of 680 and 3x the rent gross monthly income.', 'No pets and No smoking.']
